data.title: 555 Victorian magistrate cleared of wrongdoing over relationship with court clerk
data.desc: An investigation clears Rodney Higgins of wrongdoing after he was accused by the Shadow Attorney General of lacking judicial independence during his relationship with a young court clerk.
